description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Sakura purrs with a rating of 89, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 178, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 5 for East, 5 for South, and 1 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10892-65510-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
